						               													<description>A box full of surprises, three exciting time travel adventures and a unique combination of quiz questions and escape feeling - that's QUIZscape! The game box is a time machine with which the players must complete three adventures. The novel game concept by Arno Steinwender alternates various puzzles with quiz questions: Wrong answers increase the time pressure! And the game is full of surprises. The title trams&amp;ouml;ates to &amp;quot;The Golden Letter&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The 1st stop on the journey through time takes the players to medieval Mainz. None other than Johannes Gutenberg needs help.&amp;#10;The 2nd adventure takes the players to 18th century Venice on the trail of Casanova.&amp;#10;The 3rd adventure takes the players to the United States: In the middle of the Cold War, the first manned moon landing is in danger.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is suitable for beginners and offers a quick start. Everyone can start puzzling right away in just a few steps.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play:&amp;#10;The players play together through 3 different adventures. In the process, they have to answer quiz questions and solve puzzles. Additional clues and secret messages are hidden in the box. But be careful: time is running out, and time is deducted for each incorrectly answered quiz question.&amp;#10;Can the players find the clues and solve the questions and puzzles?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
